# ── Optional map tile upgrade ────────────────────────────────────────────────
# KnowYourCity works with ZERO keys using Esri World Imagery satellite tiles.
# If you want crisper/higher-zoom satellite imagery, get a FREE Mapbox token
# (no credit card required for the free tier) at https://account.mapbox.com/
# and set it below. When present, the app uses Mapbox Satellite; otherwise it
# falls back to Esri World Imagery automatically.
#
# NOTE: Vite only exposes vars prefixed with VITE_ to the browser. This token
# WILL be visible in the shipped JS bundle (that is unavoidable for a static
# client-side app). Restrict the token to your domain(s) in the Mapbox
# dashboard (URL restrictions) so it can't be reused elsewhere.
#
# Copy this file to `.env.local` (gitignored) and fill in the value.

VITE_MAPBOX_TOKEN=

# ── Optional in-app bug reporting ────────────────────────────────────────────
# When set, the "Report a bug" form POSTs reports to this serverless endpoint,
# which files a GitHub issue for you (see worker/). Leave blank to fall back to
# opening a prefilled GitHub "new issue" page instead. Deploy the worker and put
# its URL here, e.g. https://kyl-bug.<you>.workers.dev
VITE_BUG_ENDPOINT=

# Optional Cloudflare Turnstile SITE key (public). When set, the bug form shows a
# bot check. Pair it with the worker's TURNSTILE_SECRET. See worker/README.md.
VITE_TURNSTILE_SITEKEY=

# ── Optional page-view analytics ─────────────────────────────────────────────
# Cloudflare Web Analytics beacon token (public; it ships in the client JS by
# design). Create a site under Cloudflare dashboard → Web Analytics and paste
# its token here. Cookieless — no consent banner needed. Leave blank to disable
# (e.g. local dev). In production this comes from the repo Variable
# VITE_CF_BEACON_TOKEN (see docs/OPERATIONS.md).
VITE_CF_BEACON_TOKEN=

# ── Optional anonymous daily leaderboard ─────────────────────────────────────
# When set, finishing the OFFICIAL daily challenge submits your total to this
# endpoint (the worker/leaderboard.mjs function, backed by Cloudflare D1) and the
# results screen shows "you placed Xth of Y today". Anonymous — no accounts, no
# names. Shuffle/date-override games are never submitted. Leave blank to disable
# (the standing line is simply omitted). Deploy the worker and put its URL here,
# e.g. https://kyc-leaderboard.<you>.workers.dev — see worker/README.md.
VITE_LEADERBOARD_ENDPOINT=
